name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: At the End of the Day No More

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gets rid of 'at the end of the day'

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Are you tired of the phrase "at the end of the day"? Are you always slightly confused by what the person means by that? Well, you don't have to see it any more after installing this extension, which will convert "at the end of the day" randomly into one of seven possible other phrases, like "according to the rand in Grandpa's will", or "as any junior marketing consultant could tell you".
